---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Overview
---

<div class="page">

<div class="dark-hero">
  <div class="dark-hero-inner">
    <div class="dark-hero-text">
      <div class="dateline">Primary Source Archive · Initiated April 2026 · Active Collection · D Co. 2nd Bn. 8th Cavalry · 1st Cav Div (Airmobile)</div>
      <div class="hero-hed">Delta<br><span>Company</span><br>Archive</div>
      <div class="hero-deck">A permanent record of the men of D Co., 2/8 CAV — built one soldier at a time from the materials families have kept.</div>
      <div class="hero-body">This archive collects primary source materials — letters, photographs, documents, firsthand accounts — from veterans and families of Delta Company. Compiled by the son of SGT Marvin Dale Miller, Cat Platoon, December 1970–1971.</div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <div class="hero-stat-n">{{ collections.soldiers | length }}</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-l">Soldier Profiles</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <div class="hero-stat-n">3</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-l">Combat Events</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <div class="hero-stat-n">8</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-l">KIA Documented</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <div class="hero-stat-n">2</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-l">Primary Sources</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-hero-side">
      <div class="side-label">
        {% if collections.soldiers | length == 1 %}
          Soldier Profile
        {% else %}
          Latest Profiles
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% for soldier in collections.soldiers | sort(false, false, 'name') | slice(0, 3) %}
        <a class="side-card" href="/soldiers/{{ soldier.slug }}/" style="{% if not loop.last %}margin-bottom:10px;{% endif %}">
          <div class="side-init">
            {% set parts = soldier.name.split(' ') %}
            {{ parts[0][0] }}{{ parts[1][0] if parts[1] }}{{ parts[2][0] if parts[2] }}
          </div>
          <div class="side-name">{{ soldier.name }}</div>
          <div class="side-rank">{{ soldier.rank }} · {{ soldier.platoon }}</div>
          <div class="side-field">
            <div class="side-fl">In-Country</div>
            <div class="side-fv">{{ soldier.arrived }} – {{ soldier.departed }}</div>
          </div>
          {% if soldier.decorations %}
            <div class="side-medals">
              {% for dec in soldier.decorations %}
                {% if dec.distinguished %}
                  <span class="side-medal">{{ dec.name }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="side-see">View profile</div>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
      <div class="side-notice">Contact details for living veterans are held in restricted access only and do not appear in any public view.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="body-grid">
  <div class="body-col">
    <div class="col-head">Documented Events</div>
    <div class="col-item">
      <div class="col-item-date">20 April 1971 · North of FSB Fanning</div>
      <div class="col-item-title">Contact — Bunker Complex</div>
      <div class="col-item-body">Cat Platoon spotted enemy at a creek. Range Platoon walked into a fortified bunker complex. <em class="col-hl">4 KIA.</em> Multiple accounts preserved without editorial reconciliation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-item">
      <div class="col-item-date">24 April 1971 · FSB Fontaine</div>
      <div class="col-item-title">Huey Crash — Only Known Photos</div>
      <div class="col-item-body">UH-1 crashed shortly after departure. <em class="col-hl">3 KIA.</em> SGT Miller's photographs are the only known visual record.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-item">
      <div class="col-item-date">21 October 1971 · Location Under Research</div>
      <div class="col-item-title">Contact — Makowski KIA</div>
      <div class="col-item-body">SP4 Makowski killed in action. <em class="col-hl">1 KIA.</em> Circumstances under ongoing research.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="body-col">
    <div class="col-head">Primary Sources</div>
    <div class="col-item">
      <div class="col-item-title">McGrew Field Calendar, 1971</div>
      <div class="col-item-body">Handwritten daily field notes by SGT Howard McGrew. Covers January through December 1971. Cross-referenced with letters and unit records.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-item">
      <div class="col-item-title">ASA Newsletters, 1988–2026</div>
      <div class="col-item-body">38 years of correspondence from the Association of Survivors. Names, accounts, and contact information for D Co. veterans.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="body-col">
    <div class="col-head">About This Archive</div>
    <div class="col-item-body" style="font-family:'Crimson Pro',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--dim);">
      All records are works in progress. Personal contact details for living veterans are maintained in restricted access only. Submissions from veterans, family members, and researchers are welcomed — all materials are reviewed before publication.
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:20px;">
      <a href="/contribute/" class="btn-cta" style="font-size:14px;padding:9px 20px;">Contribute →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
